claws-mail
------------------------------------------
Claws Mail is an email client (and news reader), based on GTK+, 
featuring:

* Quick response
* Graceful, and sophisticated interface
* Easy configuration, intuitive operation
* Abundant features
* Extensibility
* Robustness and stability

Lots of extra functionality, like an RSS aggregator, calendar, or laptop 
LED handling, are provided by extra plugins.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.5-1
  crypt-1.1-1
  libcairo2-1.8.10-1
  libcompface0-1.5.2-1
  libdbus-glib_1_2-0.82-1
  libenchant1-1.6.0-1
  libetpan15-1.0-1
  libgcc1-4.3.4-3
  libgcrypt11-1.4.5-1
  libgdk_pixbuf2.0_0-2.18.6-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.22.4-2
  libgnutls26-2.8.3-1
  libgtk2.0_0-2.18.6-1
  libICE6-1.0.6-1
  libiconv2-1.13.1-1
  libintl8-0.17-11
  libopenldap2_3_0-2.3.43-1
  libpango1.0_0-1.26.2-1
  libSM6-1.1.1-1
  libstartup-notification1_0-0.10-1
(bogofilter plugin)
  bogofilter
(pgp* plugins)
  libgpg-error0-1.7-1
  libgpgme11-1.1.8-2
(spamassassin plugin)
  spamassassin
(trayicon plugin)
  libX11_6-1.3.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
