Canonical website:
  http://www.gnome.org/

Canonical download:
  ftp://ftp.gnome.org/pub/gnome/sources/claws-mail/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack claws-mail-3.7.6-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./claws-mail-3.7.6-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/claws-mail-3.7.6-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/claws-mail-3.7.6-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/claws-mail-bogofilter-3.7.6-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/claws-mail-pgpcore-3.7.6-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/claws-mail-pgpinline-3.7.6-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/claws-mail-pgpmime-3.7.6-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/claws-mail-smime-3.7.6-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/claws-mail-spamassassin-3.7.6-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/claws-mail-trayicon-3.7.6-X.tar.bz2

